OL,6,FA Greater Manchester detective, who
OL,7,Fwas jailed for sexual assault, has
OL,8,Fbeen dismissed and barred from
OL,9,Fpolicing after a misconduct hearing
OL,10,Fheard he preyed on women at work.
OL,12,FDetective Sergeant Richard Mills was
OL,13,Fsentenced in December to 18 months in
OL,14,Fprison after a jury found him guilty
OL,15,Fof two counts of sexual assault.
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police said there
OL,18,Fwere numerous other allegations made
OL,19,Fagainst Mills that amounted to
OL,20,Fbreaches of its code of ethics and
OL,21,Fstandards of professional behaviour.
