OL,6,FDetective Superintendent David Jones,
OL,7,Ffrom the force's professional
OL,8,Fstandards directorate, said an
OL,9,Finternal investigation "uncovered
OL,10,Falarming circumstances" of Mills'
OL,11,Fbehaviour.
OL,13,FHe said, "Mills sexually assaulted his
OL,14,Fcolleagues, made inappropriate remarks
OL,15,Fof a sexual nature and acted in a
OL,16,Fdisgraceful manner."
