OL,6,FMills was based in GMP's Oldham
OL,7,Fdistrict and at GMP's serious crime
OL,8,Fdirectorate at Nexus House in Ashton-
OL,9,Funder-Lyne when the criminal offences
OL,10,Ftook place.
OL,12,FHe was convicted at Liverpool Crown
OL,13,FCourt of two incidents of forceful
OL,14,Fsexual touching in 2016 and 2020.
OL,16,FSentencing him, Judge David Swinnerton
OL,17,Fsaid Mills, of Oakley Way, Wardle,
OL,18,FRochdale, had taken advantage of a
OL,19,Fculture within the lower ranks of the
OL,20,Fforce of not reporting officers.
