OL,6,FIn a statement, one of the victims
OL,7,Fasked, "How do you call the police
OL,8,Fabout the police?"
OL,10,FShe added, "I used to be such a happy,
OL,11,Fsmiley and bubbly character and I feel
OL,12,Fthe complete opposite. I just feel sad
OL,13,Fall the time."
OL,15,FProfessional standards began
OL,16,Finvestigating Mills in 2016, and again
OL,17,Fin March 2023 following complaints
OL,18,Ffrom colleagues about him making
OL,19,Finappropriate comments.
