OL,6,FDet Supt Jones added, "Our
OL,7,Finvestigation into DS Mills uncovered
OL,8,Falarming circumstances, whereby he
OL,9,Fpreyed on women in the workplace who
OL,10,Fwere simply just trying to do their
OL,11,Fjobs.
OL,13,F"He abused his position in the force
OL,14,Fand the trust of his colleagues for
OL,15,Fhis own perverse gratification.
OL,17,F"Mills' actions continue to have an
OL,18,Fadverse impact on many of our staff
OL,19,Fand officers who have been offered
OL,20,Fspecialist support.
