OL,6,F"It is our hope today's outcome
OL,7,Fprovided closure to those who may have
OL,8,Fbeen seeking it, as well as
OL,9,Freassurance that when allegations are
OL,10,Fraised, they will be thoroughly
OL,11,Finvestigated and outcomes pursued.
OL,13,F"The actions of Mill's are
OL,14,Freprehensible, and there is no place
OL,15,Ffor him in policing.
